text: Fahad Al-Azmi is a member of the Kuwaiti National Assembly, representing the fifth district. Born in 1954, Al-Azmi worked in the Interior Ministry before being elected to the National Assembly in 1999. Al-Azmi is considered an Independent and is on good terms with the royal family. He is a member of the Al-Awazem tribe.Arab Times MP Profile ==References== Category:Kuwaiti people of Arab descent Category:Members of the National Assembly of Kuwait Category:Living people Category:1954 births Category:Government ministers of Kuwait
